              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  The activity measurements were performed more",
                " than 1.5 years after the irradiation, using a high",
                " efficiency Ge detector (115% relative to a 3 by",
                " 3 inch NaI detector). The gamma-ray spectra were ana-",
                " lyzed using the genie code system. The detector effi-",
                " ciency was calibrated to a precision of about 3%",
                " using standard gamma-ray sources."
              ]
            }
          ],
